10.000Z","msg":"又係一種惡習<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/01/100354_010594002f1c3913860211dcd6466209.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F01%2F100354_010594002f1c3913860211dcd6466209.png&h=083b083f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"270633b1f12545a3ce1c24d81213fb1eb973a197","tid":763001,"uid":6959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T02:17:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6be8a64cb4d6ca17b164e4aafc76e220f4d9215b","tid":763001,"uid":22568,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f9a0ea80c778a63482d2297beb130ae7f8a6336a","tid":763001,"uid":195479,"like":71,"dislike":5,"score":66,"quote":{"pid":"90f7640e66bdc6c9cfe7602a012c693f35cac55e","tid":763001,"uid":89134,"like":7,"dislike":13,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T18:21:07.000Z","msg":"大陸人"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T18:21:47.000Z","msg":"香港人都有"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T02:27:39.000Z","msg":"此post已完"},{"pid":"6fc31080953acceac10580a43fdfd0f9061b6928","tid":763001,"uid":19552,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"quote":{"pid":"270633b1f12545a3ce1c24d81213fb1eb973a197","tid":763001,"uid":6959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T02:17:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T02:58:26.000Z","msg":"[img]<a href=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20130829/small/29la8p3.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20130829%2Fsmall%2F29la8p3.jpg&d=W67X%2BWn2kt8mU7f9FemoogRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=cbbd07be\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20130829%2Fsmall%2F29la8p3.jpg&h=9f1ef778\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20130829/small/29la8p3.jpg</a><br />\n[/img]<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/ZprpGpR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FZprpGpR.jpg&h=71794b87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n46歲的男導遊霍俊傑趁工作之便，在12年至13年間多次在赤鱲角機場的行李輸送帶上順手牽羊，偷走其他旅客共12個名牌RIMOWA行李箱，最後被埋伏的警員當場拘捕，今在荃灣法院承認共12項盜竊罪，押後至7月22日等候心理及背景報告再判刑，被告還柙小欖。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n住公屋經常搭車去豪宅附近打卡"},{"pid":"50310ee512dba801d190f376108b4cc6bfc3f5ab","tid":763001,"uid":19552,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T03:00:42.000Z","msg":"涉偷篋領隊愛fb炫富 <br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】化身「名篋神偷」狂偷貴價篋的旅行團領隊落網後，旋即被網民大起底，揭發他常於facebook（fb）晒命炫富，將多張鑽戒、名錶及名牌手袋照片放上網，聲稱是送給妻子的「新玩具」，當中包括10多個疑似賊贓的德國名牌RIMOWA行李篋，網民質疑其妻亦是幫兇。永安旅行社證實一名領隊涉偷竊被捕，案件已交由警方處理，不便評論。 <br />\n<br />\n妻被懷疑是幫兇 <br />\n被捕46歲領隊姓霍，已任職領隊10多年，昨天獲准保釋候查。事件曝光後網民即大起底，發現與妻子居於澤安邨的霍，經常於住所毗鄰的豪宅帝景峰「打卡」，並上載名錶及名牌手袋等照片，加上經常帶貴價歐洲團，<span style=\"color: red;\">生活看似富貴，被友人稱為「霍公子」</span>。 <br />\n霍的facebook內不時上載名牌物品相，最矚目莫過於一張於7月10日上載，一張14個紅、銀、紫及黑色RIMOWA行李篋的相片，報稱是在家中拍攝。仔細查看，發現該批行李篋，與前天他被押返住所搜獲的相似。本月內，他先後上載一張巨型紅寶石鑽戒、名牌手錶和一張有10個COACH、Vivienne Westwood等名牌手袋的相片，聲稱是買給妻子的「新玩具」，但名袋明顯是二手貨。 <br />\n有網民質疑全部貴價貨均是賊贓，更懷疑其妻亦是幫兇。執業大律師陸偉雄稱，即使不知情，但在「忽然富貴」、「物件新舊」的合理懷疑下，有人仍接受物品，可能構成處理贓物罪。霍過去一年多次出團返港後，於機場行李輸送帶偷去13個德國名牌RIMOWA行李篋，前天重施故技，被埋伏機場警員人贓並獲。"},{"pid":"a7b9dde2fe8943752fac2609bea8f168da09666a","tid":763001,"uid":177719,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T03:00:53.000Z","msg":"咁其實炫耀呢個行為本身就係自卑心作祟而衍生出黎既"},{"pid":"42d2934398c099397d4599000c92bb2f43817c81","tid":763001,"uid":177719,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"a7b9dde2fe8943752fac2609bea8f168da09666a","tid":763001,"uid":177719,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T03:00:53.000Z","msg":"咁其實炫耀呢個行為本身就係自卑心作祟而衍生出黎既"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T03:02:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">虛</span></strong>榮</span>"},{"pid":"429cff978788a6c3b8afc52a90a43172713d3f3b","tid":763001,"uid":195479,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"42d2934398c099397d4599000c92bb2f43817c81","tid":763001,"uid":177719,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"a7b9dde2fe8943752fac2609bea8f168da09666a","tid":763001,"uid":177719,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T03:00:53.000Z","msg":"咁其實炫耀呢個行為本身就係自卑心作祟而衍生出黎既"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T03:02:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">虛</span></strong>榮</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T04:24:36.000Z","msg":"長期用虛榮黎換取滿足感<br />\n真係可恥<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eec559241a2a7d92e02a12cbc6818a639fa0a24a","tid":763001,"uid":195479,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"6be8a64cb4d6ca17b164e4aafc76e220f4d9215b","tid":763001,"uid":22568,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f9a0ea80c778a63482d2297beb130ae7f8a6336a","tid":763001,"uid":195479,"like":71,"dislike":5,"score":66,"quote":{"pid":"90f7640e66bdc6c9cfe7602a012c693f35cac55e","tid":763001,"uid":89134,"like":7,"dislike":13,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T18:21:07.000Z","msg":"大陸人"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T18:21:47.000Z","msg":"香港人都有"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T02:27:39.000Z","msg":"此post已完"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T04:26:19.000Z","msg":"唔容許香港人評論香港人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2769ea7ae5b4a493a5d211e2a62fd1b75d2eedc","tid":763001,"uid":154106,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T09:49:56.000Z","msg":"炫咪炫囉 最多唔睇 <br />\n利申 成日炫開"},{"pid":"57efc294de8798efebbcd95f179f8f713187d317","tid":763001,"uid":3028,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T09:54:50.000Z","msg":"李嘉誠都係戴幾千蚊既錶<br />\n係得班窮撚死都要戴撈<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.